ABOUT US:
ICI Contracting is a well-known, established company in Commercial Renovation and construction industry. With its founder having over 20 years of experience in the construction and renovation of various buildings. ICI has enjoyed working with major industry-leading suppliers, architects, and engineers specializing in the commercial, industrial, hospitality, and residential industries.
With research & development always progressing forward to exceed today’s performance requirements, ICI Contracting has been able to achieve high standards and a reputation in the industry.
ICI Contracting has worked on several projects-Industrial, Commercial and Place of Worship Buildings. Our purpose is to be a leading company in this competitive industry by providing enhanced service, build relationships, and repeat clients.
To contribute to our always forward Rushing forces, we are planning to add an experienced Sales Representative and Marketing specialist to our dedicated team;
Responsibilities:
Strong interpersonal and communication skills (verbal, written, presentation);
Various sales techniques; identifying prospects and referral sources while developing and maintaining excellent relationships;
The ability to negotiate with clients to “close the sale”;
The ability to consistently achieve, if not exceed, sales quotas;
The ability to self-motivate; a positive and energetic approach to the work and the team;
The ability to utilize MS Office applications and CRM programs.
Forecast sales and develop unique sales strategies while evaluating effectiveness;
Build and maintain productive long-lasting relationships with designers, architects, etc. for repeat and referral business leads;
Provide feedback to management using financial, and statistical data;
Attend meetings, sales events, trade shows and training to remain current with industry developments
Have at least 3 years of experience in sales, specifically in selling services;
Provide knowledge and assistance to clients, responding to inquiries while following corporate guidelines;
Provide excellence in client service, understanding the scope of their needs and resolve concerns;
Expand client database by performing selling activities using results-driven sales methods and techniques;
***This is a 100 percent commission base position***(Only the candidates who are salesman/woman by nature to apply please)
